{"tid":1669089,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(代POST)【本土X國際戰線】鍾庭耀發起全港大型民調及公投(2)","createTime":"2019-10-22T10:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T01:45:56.000Z","uid":156096,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"96b8a0693874b74c717469bb3b015dea41536c26","tid":1669089,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:55:53.000Z","msg":"上一個post：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1659927/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1659927/page/1</a><br />\n大家好，我地係一群熱愛香港的小市民<br />\n可能係上一個post 打的太多字，連登仔可能資訊疲勞，未有好大反應。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>背景</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n簡單來講，我們和鍾庭耀教授同有同一個信念，就是希望透過科學化的方法，歸納出香港人在今次反送中運動裡大大小小事件上民意。<br />\n<br />\n我們認為香港人善忘的最大原因，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">正正就是因為「核彈」太多太密集，香港人先會失焦</span></strong>。<br />\n因此，我們會在透過<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">持續追蹤核彈的民意，並且幾日就會公佈一次民調</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n持續而有系統的民調報告，可以有效提醒及向港共政權，人民地要核彈的真相同解釋!!!<br />\n首階段，我們先加入一些主流 (公認大事件721, 831)和近期核彈的民意 ；同時我們會在網上收集民間想做民調的核彈，定期更新及<ins><strong>持續追蹤這些核彈的民意</strong></ins>。<br />\n<br />\n最後，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">當核彈的民意是持續一段時間，而本土民憤不減，即使日日核爆，香港人都沒有忘記重要的核彈。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>舉個例子大家，</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wtVZZXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwtVZZXA.jpg&h=6b8df69f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>點解張建宗要社會向前看??? </strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>因為佢知道721 831 才是整個反送中運動的真核彈，是一粒足夠令政府大敗的核彈，政府最希望就是人民不要再提，務求冷卻事件的嚴重性</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">運用鍾庭耀教授在國際的名望同影響力，民調過後將會有一份完整而科學化的報告向世界各國宣傳香港人的長時間民意及呼叫。<br />\n這將會是一份最強的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>國際文宣</ins></span>，要全世界都向港共政權交代核彈真相!!!</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>和理非可以做d 咩???</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1)在香港民意研究計劃網頁上<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><ins>定期提交香港人想調查的核彈的民情 (我們會按不同時機不斷追蹤最強核彈和換入新核彈)</ins></span></span></strong><br />\n2)<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><ins>幫手眾籌</ins></strong></span></span> (從10月17日起計至2019年12月底，所需要的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><ins>費用大約為港幣80萬元</ins></span></strong></span>，超額的話會用作2020年【我們香港人】的延續經費)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uB22dmg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuB22dmg.jpg&h=c1b97c0d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n3) <ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Subscribe 香港民意研究所</span></span></strong></ins> Facebook 和 Youtube<br />\n<br />\nLINK﹕<br />\n香港民意研究所 Facebook﹕​​​​​​​<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKPublicOpinionProgram/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKPublicOpinionProgram%2F&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU99ps0HX4IqOCTpD1RfAd9E%3D&h=80455294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKPublicOpinionProgram/</a><br />\n香港民意研究所 Youtube﹕ <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCxNv1rm97xhk-3zN9kvAOKw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCxNv1rm97xhk-3zN9kvAOKw&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU99ps0HX4IqOCTpD1RfAd9E%3D&h=ad6bcf70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCxNv1rm97xhk-3zN9kvAOKw</a><br />\n香港民意研究計劃 (香港民研) 網頁﹕<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/wehkers-index\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fwehkers-index&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU99ps0HX4IqOCTpD1RfAd9E%3D&h=7e6ebdcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/wehkers-index</a> (<strong><ins>有是次調查的簡介﹑提交問題方法﹑眾籌LINK</ins></strong>)<br />\n<br />\n最後，補多句╴<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">現在放棄的話 比賽就結束了!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rnddj4J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frnddj4J.jpg&h=6cb67c51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49eb9905c719b82ed3904cfa56a4f9e1957e3d32","tid":1669089,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:56:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"621eb40c379b0ac782ecb6fafe6019532aa92bd0","tid":1669089,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:56:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b2abd8412def1f06853692b047b45abec4dea74","tid":1669089,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:56:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"501a3c8d6aeb1e83c6cd623c1a30026e69a3cdb4","tid":1669089,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:57:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f8b1fc667898024c71e36661aca8bb7e5876eca","tid":1669089,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:57:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4c39c2bf7405ec2abfcdfe43df04b267fab6901","tid":1669089,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:58:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cbe636a9ce46eb96e4540180249ad53441920ee7","tid":1669089,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:58:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcb463aebb8b5ea993a0e6e941102461853cddf9","tid":1669089,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:59:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e3c15046ef95196494a5039aa8d85f6496f9082","tid":1669089,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:59:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ef281e3e77fc923593b1a069e512c59b31e1f02","tid":1669089,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,